### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### ================================================
### ADMINISTRADORES - CRUD Completo
### ================================================

### 1. CREAR nuevo Administrador
POST {{baseUrl}}/admins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dni": "1",
  "name": "Adrián",
  "surName": "Fernández",
  "tele": "5551112222",
  "pass": "adminPassword123"
}

### 2. OBTENER todos los Administradores
GET {{baseUrl}}/admins
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. ACTUALIZAR Administrador por DNI
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admins/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Adrián Maximiliano",
  "surName": "Fernández López",
  "tele": "5559998888"
}

### 4. ELIMINAR Administrador por DNI
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admins/1
Content-Type: application/json

